Saying the truth,agt is all about singers and magician. It shouldn't be named as a talent show. I agree that singing is also a talent but seriously, why people only choose those whom they can relate. Talent should be about how good a person can do a thing and how much he is skilled in a thing. Everyone supports people like shin lim,darcy lynne, grace vanderwaal, kodi lee just because they knows about singing and like to see magic(just like a child).But i remember a guy named lee ridley.He was a talent in a true sense. Of course he won bgt and get a shot at agt champions season 1(eliminated in preliminary round) but he didn't get any other chance like these people just because a so called legend simon cowell (with due respect) may be don't want to recognize him(I believe he deserved to be in finals). This is the bitter truth. I am an indian and i should support v unbeatable and i really do. But its all about talent and we can't choose a talent based over his or her origin, race,color.
I am writing this just because (i think) no one was writing what it is actually all about. Many people still dislike this comment because of what i wrote or may be based on the fact that i am an indian.I didn't write all this just for some likes but just so that may be one out of a million people would read and understand this.

So, maybe folks should boycot the AGT show also.
